text: Entlebuch is a district of the canton of Lucerne in Switzerland. The capital is the municipality of Schüpfheim. == Municipalities == It contains the following municipalities: * Doppleschwand * Entlebuch * Escholzmatt * Flühli * Hasle * Marbach * Romoos * Schüpfheim * Werthenstein == References ==
title: Entlebuch District
